    {
      "type": "p",
      "id": "b0",
      "text": "The office had emptied by the time [[justice|Justice]] turned its attention to her."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "id": "b1",
      "text": "Marcella had carried the project alone. She did not expect the glass to open."
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "id": "b2",
      "text": "The glass opened without sound."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "id": "b3",
      "text": "What the room had hidden, the light now made plain."
    }
  ],
